Package: bolsec
Type: Package
Title: Bolivian Securities 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alvaro Ignacio Tapia 
Maintainer: Alvaro Ignacio Tapia <alvaroignaciotapia@gmail.com>
Description: Provides data import and offers 3 daily snaphot functions from securities of varying prices traded on the Bolivian Securities Exchange (Bolsa Boliviana de Valores). The snapshots include a detailed list, scatter plot correlation, and descriptive statistics table for the securities.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Website: "https://www.bbv.com.bo"
Imports: dplyr, rvest, formattable, stats, graphics
Suggests: knitr,rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr


